'''南非國防軍'''（{{lang-af|Suid-Afrikaanse Nasionale Weermag}}，{{lang-en|'''S'''outh '''A'''frican '''N'''ational '''D'''efence '''F'''orce}}，簡稱為'''SANDF'''）是[[南非|南非]]的[[軍隊|軍隊]]。南非國防軍指揮官由[[南非總統|南非總統]]從其中一個部隊中任命，其亦須向{{le|國防部 (南非)|Department of Defence (South Africa)|國防部}}的{{le|國防部長與退伍軍人|Minister of Defence and Military Veterans}}負責。

現今的南非國防軍於1994年[[南非種族隔離|種族隔離]]結束後第一次全國大選以及通過新憲法後建軍<ref name="constitution-1993-224">{{cite web |url=http://www.info.gov.za/documents/constitution/93cons.htm#SECTION224 |title=Constitution of the Republic of South Africa Act 200 of 1993 (Section 224) |accessdate=2008-06-23 |year=1993 |publisher=South African Government |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080612100516/http://www.info.gov.za/documents/constitution/93cons.htm#SECTION224 |archive-date=2008-06-12 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.issafrica.org/Pubs/ASR/6No2/VanStade.html |title=Rationalisation in the SANDF: The Next Challenge |accessdate=2008-06-23 |year=1997 |author=L B van Stade |publisher=Institute for Security Studies |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160316204323/https://issafrica.org/pubs/asr/6no2/vanstade.html |archivedate=2016-03-16 }}</ref>。其取代了實施種族隔離時以白人為主的{{le|南非防衛軍|South African Defence Force}}，並與[[民族之矛|民族之矛]]游擊隊整合。

== 歷史 ==
南非國防軍是整合自南非防衛軍<ref name="2h">{{cite web |url=http://humanities.ufs.ac.za/dl/userfiles/Documents/00001/1093_eng.pdf |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-10-21 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130801082203/http://humanities.ufs.ac.za/dl/userfiles/Documents/00001/1093_eng.pdf |archivedate=2013-08-01 }}</ref>及一些民間的[[武裝力量|武裝力量]]，例如政黨[[非洲人國民大會|非洲人國民大會]]的游擊部隊[[民族之矛|民族之矛]]<ref name="constitution-1993-224" />和一些地方武力<ref name="2h" />。截至2004年，南非國防軍上述的整合過程被認為是成功的，而且人員和結構也很完整；然而，近年來由於財政緊縮，整合引致的問題逐漸浮現，令戰鬥力下降<ref>U.S. Embassy The Hague, [http://www.wikileaks.ch/cable/2005/11/05THEHAGUE2973.html 05THEHAGUE2973 Netherlands/Africa: DASD Whelan's visit to The Hague] {{Wayback|url=http://www.wikileaks.ch/cable/2005/11/05THEHAGUE2973.html |date=20111111220459 }}, 2005</ref>。1999年，南非政府使用四百八十億[[美元|美元]]購買武器裝備<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ifp.org.za/Newsletters/071122wn.htm |title=Mangosuthu Buthelezi's Weekly Newsletter to the Nation |date=22 November 2007 |publisher=[[Inkatha_Freedom_Party|Inkatha Freedom Party]] |work=Ifp.org.za |accessdate=2008-11-13 |first=Mangosuthu |last=Buthelezi |authorlink=Mangosuthu Buthelezi |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081203170352/http://www.ifp.org.za/Newsletters/071122wn.htm |archivedate=2008-12-03 }}</ref><ref name=rotten>[http://www.guardian.co.uk/commentisfree/2007/jan/10/somethingisrotten Bright hopes betrayed] {{Wayback|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/commentisfree/2007/jan/10/somethingisrotten |date=20121114044128 }} Mail & Guardian</ref>，收購護衛艦、潛艇、輕型多用途直升機、殲擊[[教練機|教練機]]以及輕型[[戰機|戰機]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.issafrica.org/uploads/ENEETHLING15_4.PDF |title=African Security Review 15.4 |accessdate=2014-07-07 |archive-date=2013-12-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131230235251/http://www.issafrica.org/uploads/ENEETHLING15_4.PDF |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 結構 ==
南非國防軍隸屬於{{link-en|南非國防部|Department of Defence (South Africa)}}<ref name="org">{{Cite web |url=http://www.dod.mil.za/documents/strategicbusinessplan/Strategic%20Business%20Plan%202009.pdf |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-07-07 |archive-date=2014-07-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714203819/http://www.dod.mil.za/documents/strategicbusinessplan/Strategic%20Business%20Plan%202009.pdf |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，下有四個武裝部隊，包括{{link-en|南非軍隊衛生服務|South African Military Health Service}}、{{link-en|南非陸軍|South African Army}}、{{link-en|南非海軍|South African Navy}}以及[[南非空軍|南非空軍]]<ref name="org"/>（不包括{{link-en|南非特種部隊|South African Special Forces}}）。

== 任務 ==
南非國防軍負責國內多項保安任務，例如維護邊境安全、救災、確保大型體育賽事的安全（如[[2013年非洲國家盃|2013年非洲國家盃]]）<ref name="2012Deploy">{{cite web | url=http://www.dod.mil.za/news/2012/11/cjops.htm | title=C J OPS Briefs Media on Deployments | accessdate=22 January 2013 | archive-date=2012-12-19 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121219042305/http://www.dod.mil.za/news/2012/11/cjops.htm | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

